general_info: Zelman Development Co is a privately owned commercial real estate development company headquartered in Los Angeles, California. Founded in the early 1960's our company originally specialized in industrial property development in and around the greater Los Angeles area. Through the years we have expanded these efforts to include suburban office, airport parking facilities, and large format power retail shopping centers. Zelman Development Co has specific expertise in developing properties requiring extensive rezoning or new entitlement. Zelman's success in completing complex entitlements and Environmental Impact Reports is one of its strongest calling cards, helping create a reputation for working well with local businesses and city officials in designing and completing projects complimentary to the surrounding environment. Zelman Development Co.'s success is due in large measure to a very experienced group of senior executives with a broad range of expertise in development, architecture, construction management, financing, law, and entitlements. The company has formed longstanding tenant relationships with industry leaders such as, Lowe's Home Improvement, and Kohl's. Our success is due in large part to these relationships and our ability to attract capital from major financial institutions. This has allowed us build a solid portfolio of highly successful commercial properties that will provide us the liquidity and financial stability necessary to build on our past success. Zelman Development Co conducts many of its business activities under the names Zelman Retail Partners, Inc and Zelman Industrial Partners, Inc. The Zelman Companies are located at 515 So. Figueroa Street, CA 90071 Los Angeles Suite 1230 The offices can be reached by phone at 213 ) 533-8100 or by fax at 213 ) 533-8118.

general_info: LAEDC is also known as Los Angeles Economic Development Corporation. Established in 1981, it is a private, nonprofit business organization. LAEDC provides more than $100 million annual tax revenue benefits to local government and educational institutes in Los Angeles. The organization provides a range of business and job opportunities. It offers various business assistance services, such as work force development, financial assistance and project management. LAEDC also provides economic information and consulting services. The organization additionally promotes various programs and initiatives, such as the Center of Economic Development, which is a regional business program. It provides data on various industries in the region and publishes an e-mail newsletter, The e-EDGE.

general_info: With over 30 years of retail, office, industrial, and housing development experience, Bakewell Company has grown into one of the largest and oldest privately owned African American real estate development and media companies in the United States. In the last ten years, Bakewell Company has ventured into the media business with the purchase of the Los Angeles Sentinel Newspaper and WBOK 1230 Am in New Orleans. In addition, keeping up with new media trends, Bakewell Company has launched www.lasentinel.net and www.wbok1230am.com. Founded in the late 70's by the company's Chairman & CEO Danny J. Bakewell, Sr., Bakewell Company has built its reputation by creating world class development projects in urban and underdeveloped communities throughout California using a qualified and experienced development team that also is representative of the very people who live and ultimately patronize the projects they are developing. Now lead by Danny J. Bakewell Jr., the company's President and COO, Bakewell Company has a full time staff along with a number of part time employees, consultants, and contracted service providers working as part of company's development staff. Bakewell Company is a full service real estate development company, operating in the State of California as a Limited Liability Company. Bakewell Company has developed, built, sold and/or managed over 4, 000, 000 square feet of retail, office, industrial, and housing projects. Bakewell Company's developments have often become the cornerstone and catalyst for community revitalization and economic investment throughout California. Having the vision and foresight to believe in an area long before others have the courage to develop is the hallmark of Bakewell Company. Believing in the residents of a community and being committed to giving those residents the resources that are afforded other communities is what puts Bakewell Company in a class all its own.

general_info: Cumming Corporation is a full-service construction consultancy firm that offers a wide range of project management services. It serves government agencies, owners, developers, architects, attorneys, and financial and educational institutions. The company provides cost estimation and planning services that include economic analysis, constructability reviews, banking assistance and value engineering. It also offers risk identification and management services for schools, hospitals, public facilities, and industrial and retail buildings. Additionally, the company undertakes repair and renovation of existing buildings. It also offers scheduling services for a wide variety of construction projects. Cumming Corporation has offices throughout California, Texas, Colorado and Arizona.

general_info: Cadiz is a publicly held land and water resource management company that specializes in the areas of groundwater storage and supply, water-conserving irrigation and desert agriculture. Its portfolio of assets encompasses landholdings with groundwater resources and water storage availability, agricultural water rights, crops in production, and technologies for water conservation, reclamation, production and conveyance. In total, Cadiz owns approximately 46,000 acres throughout Southern California, all in close proximity to the state s aqueduct system. Cadiz was founded in 1983 and has corporate headquarters in Los Angeles. Its common shares are traded on the NASDAQ under the ticker symbol CDZI.

general_info: Founded in 1994, CIM Group is a full-service private equity real estate investor. It has expertise in various areas of investment and development; mezzanine financing; fund management; commercial leasing; and property management. The group offers a range of investment and development services, including acquisitions, construction management, entitlement and planning, design and architecture management, hold analysis and dispositions, and leasing and tenant management. It has a team of experts that conducts various analyses, including community and political support, property and market analyses, exit strategy, risk assessment and mitigation. Headquartered in Los Angeles, CIM Group has regional offices in San Francisco and Bethesda, Md.

general_info: Marsh is one of the world's leading risk and insurance services firms. The company employs nearly 30,000 employees and has annual revenues exceeding $5 billion. It provides its customers with a variety of services, such as worldwide risk management, risk consulting, insurance broking, financial solutions and insurance program management services for businesses, public entities, associations, professional services organizations and private clients. The firm provides advice and transactional capabilities to clients in more than 100 countries. Other services include employee practices liability, trade credit, crisis consulting, crisis academy, political risk assessment and a number of specialty Japan client services. The company is part of the family of Marsh & McLennan companies that also includes Kroll, Guy Carpenter, Putnam Investments, Mercer Human Resource Consulting and Mercer s specialty consulting businesses. Marsh is headquartered in New York, with an office in Los Angeles.

general_info: Affordable Drafting Services  Design firm has been in business since 1992 offering the lowest rates for drafting in the industry. With its success ADS is offering the same service on the private sector for single families looking to remodel, add or convert their homes. With these tough economic times ADS has decided to lower its rates even lower to earn your business.   Affordable Drafting Services is committed to providing you with the best design services available. We approach every project with a focus on aesthetics, functionality, cost, and structural engineering. For over fifteen years, ADS has been designing unique and innovative structures. Each project is handled with unique perspective and integrity. ADS is established itself as a leader in the industry. Ingenuity and an eye for solutions make ADS the obvious choice for design services.     Custom Homes and Residential Communities  If you can dream it, we can design it. Many of our master planned communities have received national recognition. We maintain control throughout the design and construction process to ensure that your residence is built to the highest quality standards. Our communities and custom homes are always exceptionally beautiful, well appointed, and extremely comfortable. We have been creating happy homeowners for over 20 years.   Commercial and Industrial Property  We manage all stages of each project. From the pre-design phase of a project through construction and delivery. We form alliances with investors, contractors, structural engineers, and specialized trades people.   ADS is known for:  ◦On schedule completion. ◦Final product exceeding expectations. ◦Honesty, integrity, and great value.

general_info: Leidenfrost/Horowitz & Associates is a firm offering architectural design services for public and private clients. Since its inception in 1976, the firm has grown to 85 professionals in three locations. The firm s portfolio includes academic facilities, retail and commercial centers, hospitality and entertainment venues, health care and government projects. Its clients include Glendale Unified School District, Los Angeles Southwest College, Irvine Unified School District, Orange Unified School District, University of California, and San Diego City Schools. The firm provides its clients with accredited in-house professionals. Leidenfrost/Horowitz & Associates specializes in neighborhood, regional mixed-use and lifestyle shopping centers serving the developer community, as well as regional and national retail chains. Leidenfrost/Horowitz & Associates is headquartered in Glendale, Calif.

general_info: CPBL is a construction company that concentrates on new construction and large renovation projects ranging in size from $10 million to $200 million. Charles Pankow Builders provides construction services to the following industries: office buildings, hotels, and resorts, retail, residential, parking, and healthcare. Its portfolio includes mall, department stores, hotels for major chains, and several of California s larger medical facilities.
